question.text: Forgot your password, boss? Resetting’s a breeze—just spot the ‘Forgot Password’ option below the login page, click it, and the system’ll walk you through it!
variations: Lupa kata laluan, boss? Reset senang je—cari pilihan ‘Lupa Kata Laluan’ kat bawah laman log masuk, klik, sistem bawa boss buat!
Forgot your password, boss? Resetting’s a breeze—just spot the ‘Forgot Password’ option below the login page, click it, and the system’ll walk you through it!
若您忘記了密碼，重設很簡單，老板！只需在登錄頁面下方找到‘忘記密碼’選項，點擊後系統會引導您進行密碼重設。

languages.en: How can I reset my password if I've forgotten it?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menetapkan semula kata laluan saya jika saya terlupa?
languages.cn: 如果我忘記了密碼，我該如何重設密碼？

detailed.en: No panic, boss! Forgot your password? Hit ‘Forgot Password’ under login—system’s got your back!
detailed.ms: Tak payah panik, boss! Lupa kata laluan? Tekan ‘Lupa Kata Laluan’ bawah log masuk—sistem tolong boss!
detailed.cn: 別急，老板！忘了密碼？登錄頁下點‘忘記密碼’，系統會帶您走！

question.text: You bet you can change your phone number, boss! Tap the profile icon at the bottom of the app, pick the phone swap option, and update away!
variations: Mesti boleh tukar nombor telefon, boss! Tekan ikon profil kat bawah app, pilih pilihan tukar telefon, kemas kini je!
You bet you can change your phone number, boss! Tap the profile icon at the bottom of the app, pick the phone swap option, and update away!
當然可以更改您的手機號碼，老板！請點擊應用程序下方的人頭圖標，然後選擇更換手機號碼的選項進行更新。

languages.en: Is it possible to change the phone number associated with my account?
languages.ms: Adakah mungkin untuk menukar nombor telefon yang dikaitkan dengan akaun saya?
languages.cn: 我可以更改與我賬戶相關的手機號碼嗎？

detailed.en: Sure thing, boss! Phone swap’s a go—profile icon at the bottom, hit the change option, bam, updated!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Tukar telefon boleh—ikon profil kat bawah, tekan pilihan tukar, bam, dah kemas kini!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！換手機號簡單，點下方人頭，選更換選項，砰，更新好！

question.text: Yep, boss—right now, our platform’s mostly locked to certain spots like Malaysia. Other countries might hit a wall. Abroad? Try a VPN to sneak in!
variations: Ya, boss—buat masa ni platform kami kebanyakannya kunci kat tempat macam Malaysia. Negara lain mungkin terhalang. Kat luar? Cuba VPN untuk masuk sembunyi!
Yep, boss—right now, our platform’s mostly locked to certain spots like Malaysia. Other countries might hit a wall. Abroad? Try a VPN to sneak in!
是的，老板，目前我們平台的訪問主要限於某些國家和地區，具體包括馬來西亞。如果您在其他國家訪問可能會受到限制。不過，若您在國外，可以嘗試使用VPN來訪問我們的平台。

languages.en: Are there any restrictions on which countries can access the games?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat sekatan pada negara mana yang boleh mengakses permainan?
languages.cn: 是否對可以訪問遊戲的國家/地區有任何限制？

detailed.en: You got it, boss! Games are Malaysia-heavy now—others might be blocked. Overseas? VPN’s your backdoor!
detailed.ms: Boleh lah, boss! Permainan fokus Malaysia sekarang—lain mungkin kena blok. Kat luar? VPN pintu belakang boss!
detailed.cn: 沒錯，老板！現在遊戲主限馬來西亞，其他地方可能不行。國外？VPN是您的後門！

question.text: You bet, boss! We’ve got a juicy loyalty program and VIP perks for regulars—every bet racks up points, and the more you pile, the sweeter the unique rewards and exclusive deals get!
variations: Mesti ada, boss! Kami ada program kesetiaan best dan faedah VIP untuk pemain tetap—setiap pertaruhan kumpul mata, lagi banyak tumpuk, lagi manis ganjaran unik dan tawaran eksklusif jadi!
You bet, boss! We’ve got a juicy loyalty program and VIP perks for regulars—every bet racks up points, and the more you pile, the sweeter the unique rewards and exclusive deals get!
當然有，老板！我們為常規玩家提供了豐富的忠誠度計劃和VIP福利。每次投注您都能獲得積分，隨着積分的累積，您可以享受各種獨特的獎勵和專屬優惠！

languages.en: Are there any loyalty programs or VIP benefits for regular players?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat program kesetiaan atau faedah VIP untuk pemain tetap?
languages.cn: 是否有針對常規玩家的忠誠度計劃或VIP福利？

detailed.en: Oh yeah, boss! Loyalty program and VIP goodies galore—bet, stack points, snag cool rewards and perks!
detailed.ms: Oh ya, boss! Program kesetiaan dan barang VIP berlambak—taruh, tumpuk mata, tangkap ganjaran dan kelebihan hebat!
detailed.cn: 當然啦，老板！忠誠計劃和VIP福利超多，投注攢積分，拿獨特獎勵和優惠哦！

question.text: Sure can, boss! A small transfer’s a slick way to test if your account’s running smooth—pick a tiny amount and watch it roll through fine!
variations: Boleh lah, boss! Pindahan kecil cara licin nak test akaun boss jalan elok—pilih jumlah kecil dan tengok masuk lancar!
Sure can, boss! A small transfer’s a slick way to test if your account’s running smooth—pick a tiny amount and watch it roll through fine!
當然可以，老板！進行小額轉賬是一個很好的方法來驗證您的賬戶是否正常運作。您可以選擇少量資金進行轉賬，以確保一切順利。

languages.en: Can I make a small transfer to verify if my account is working correctly?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya membuat pemindahan kecil untuk mengesahkan jika akaun saya berfungsi dengan betul?
languages.cn: 我可以進行小額轉賬以驗證我的賬戶是否正常運作嗎？

detailed.en: You got it, boss! Small transfer’s a neat trick—toss a bit in, see your account’s ticking right!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Pindahan kecil trik kemas—campak sikit, tengok akaun boss berjalan betul!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！小額轉賬是妙招，扔點錢進去，看您的賬戶運作順不順！

question.text: For urgent stuff, boss, hit the live support icon at the bottom of the app—our team’s there real-time to zap your issues fast!
variations: Kalau ada benda urgent, boss, tekan ikon sokongan langsung kat bawah app—pasukan kami ada secara langsung untuk hapuskan isu boss cepat!
For urgent stuff, boss, hit the live support icon at the bottom of the app—our team’s there real-time to zap your issues fast!
若您有緊急問題，老板，您可以通過應用程序下方的在線客服圖標聯繫我們。我們的客服團隊會實時為您提供幫助，確保您能迅速解決問題。

languages.en: How can I contact live support if I have urgent issues?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menghubungi sokongan langsung jika saya mempunyai isu yang mendesak?
languages.cn: 如果我有緊急問題，我如何聯繫實時支持？

detailed.en: Got a rush, boss? Tap live support at the app’s bottom—real-time crew’ll blitz your troubles quick!
detailed.ms: Ada tergesa, boss? Tekan sokongan langsung kat bawah app—pasukan masa nyata hapus masalah boss laju!
detailed.cn: 急事，老板？點應用下方的在線客服，實時團隊會快幫您解決麻煩！

question.text: Pulling funds back to your bank’s a snap, boss! Tap the wallet icon, pick ‘Withdraw,’ add your bank details if you haven’t—make sure it’s yours—punch in the amount, hit submit, and you’re rolling!
variations: Tarik dana balik ke akaun bank senang je, boss! Tekan ikon dompet, pilih ‘Pengeluaran,’ tambah butiran bank kalau belum—pastikan akaun boss—masukkan jumlah, tekan hantar, dah jalan!
Pulling funds back to your bank’s a snap, boss! Tap the wallet icon, pick ‘Withdraw,’ add your bank details if you haven’t—make sure it’s yours—punch in the amount, hit submit, and you’re rolling!
將資金提取回您的銀行賬戶的流程很簡單，老板！您只需點擊錢包圖標，然後選擇‘提款’選項。若您還沒添加銀行賬戶，請先添加您本人的賬戶信息。輸入想要提取的金額，然後點擊提交即可。

languages.en: What's the process for withdrawing funds back to my bank account?
languages.ms: Apakah proses untuk mengeluarkan dana kembali ke akaun bank saya?
languages.cn: 將資金提取回我的銀行賬戶的流程是什麼？

detailed.en: Easy, boss! Wallet icon, ‘Withdraw,’ add your bank if new—keep it yours—set amount, submit, cash is on its way!
detailed.ms: Senang je, boss! Ikon dompet, ‘Pengeluaran,’ tambah bank kalau baru—pastikan boss punya—set jumlah, hantar, duit tengah jalan!
detailed.cn: 簡單，老板！錢包圖標，‘提款’，若新加銀行—確保是您的—輸入金額，提交，錢就來了！

question.text: If your account’s at zero after a deposit, boss, first check ‘Transaction Records’ to see if it’s processed—might still be cooking. Try relogging or refreshing the page. Still zero? Send me screenshots—I’ll jump in to make sure your funds are safe!
variations: Kalau akaun boss tunjuk 0 lepas deposit, semak dulu ‘Rekod Transaksi’ tengok dah proses ke belum—mungkin tengah masak. Cuba log masuk balik atau refresh laman. Masih 0? Hantar screenshot—saya masuk pastikan duit boss selamat!

If your account’s at zero after a deposit, boss, first check ‘Transaction Records’ to see if it’s processed—might still be cooking. Try relogging or refreshing the page. Still zero? Send me screenshots—I’ll jump in to make sure your funds are safe!
若您存款後賬戶顯示為0資金，老板，首先請檢查‘交易記錄’，確認存款是否已處理，可能是還在處理中。請嘗試重新登錄或刷新頁面。若問題依然存在，請提供截圖信息，我會幫您查明情況，確保資金安全！

languages.en: What should I do if my account shows 0 credits after a deposit?
languages.ms: Apa yang harus saya lakukan jika akaun saya menunjukkan 0 kredit selepas deposit?
languages.cn: 如果存款後我的賬戶顯示為0學分，我應該怎麼做？

detailed.en: Uh-oh, boss! Zero after deposit? Peek at ‘Transaction Records’—still brewing maybe. Relog or refresh, still nada? Screenshots, I’ll lock it down!
detailed.ms: Aduh, boss! 0 lepas deposit? Tengok ‘Rekod Transaksi’—mungkin tengah masak. Log masuk balik atau refresh, masih kosong? Hantar skrin, saya kunci selamat!
detailed.cn: 哎呀，老板！存款後0錢？查‘交易記錄’，或許還在煮。重登或刷新，還沒？截圖給我，我確保安全！

question.text: Referral commission’s 3% of the new member’s total 4D bets, boss! Plus, you snag extra VIP points—the more you rope in, the juicier the haul gets!
variations: Komisen rujukan 3% dari jumlah pertaruhan 4D ahli baru, boss! Tambah lagi, boss dapat mata VIP extra—lagi banyak ajak, lagi banyak hasil kaya!
Referral commission’s 3% of the new member’s total 4D bets, boss! Plus, you snag extra VIP points—the more you rope in, the juicier the haul gets!
推薦新會員的佣金率是您推薦的4D總投資額的3%，老板！而且，您還可以獲得額外的VIP積分，推薦越多，收益也會越豐厚哦！

languages.en: What's the commission rate for referring new members?
languages.ms: Berapa kadar komisen untuk memperkenalkan ahli baru?
languages.cn: 推薦新會員的佣金率是多少？

detailed.en: Nice deal, boss! 3% off newbies’ 4D bets, plus VIP points—more you bring, more you score big!
detailed.ms: Deal mantap, boss! 3% dari pertaruhan 4D ahli baru, tambah mata VIP—lagi ramai bawa, lagi besar boss menang!
detailed.cn: 好交易，老板！新會員4D總投注3%佣金，加VIP積分，多拉多賺哦！

question.text: If you’re ready to quit playing and close your account, boss, first make sure your balance is zeroed out—then just uninstall the app, and you’re done. Can’t wait to see you back someday!
variations: Kalau boss nak berhenti main dan tutup akaun, pastikan baki boss kosong dulu—lepas tu uninstall app je, dah selesai. Tak sabar tunggu boss balik satu hari nanti!
If you’re ready to quit playing and close your account, boss, first make sure your balance is zeroed out—then just uninstall the app, and you’re done. Can’t wait to see you back someday!
若您想停止玩遊戲並關閉賬戶，老板，首先請確保您的賬戶餘額已清空。然後，您只需直接卸載我們的應用程序即可。期待未來再次與您相見！

languages.en: What's the procedure for closing my account if I wish to stop playing?
languages.ms: Apakah prosedur untuk menutup akaun saya jika saya ingin berhenti bermain?
languages.cn: 如果我想停止玩遊戲，關閉我的帳戶的流程是什麼？

detailed.en: Ready to bounce, boss? Clear your balance, ditch the app—done! Swing back anytime!
detailed.ms: Nak tarik diri, boss? Kosongkan baki, buang app—siap! Balik bila-bila lah!
detailed.cn: 想退出，老板？清空餘額，卸應用—完事！隨時回來哦！

question.text: Finding the gaming app download link’s dead easy, boss! Hit the profile icon at the app’s bottom, scroll down to the referral links part—there’s your download link, ready to roll!
variations: Cari pautan muat turun app permainan mudah gila, boss! Tekan ikon profil kat bawah app, skrol ke bahagian pautan rujukan—ada pautan muat turun boss, sedia untuk jalan!
Finding the gaming app download link’s dead easy, boss! Hit the profile icon at the app’s bottom, scroll down to the referral links part—there’s your download link, ready to roll!
要找到遊戲應用程序的下載鏈接非常簡單，老板！只需點擊應用程序下方的人頭圖標，向下滑動到推薦鏈接的部分，就能找到相關的下載鏈接。

languages.en: Where can I find the download link for the gaming app?
languages.ms: Di manakah saya boleh mencari pautan muat turun untuk aplikasi permainan?
languages.cn: 我可以在哪裡找到遊戲應用程序的下載鏈接？

detailed.en: No hassle, boss! Profile icon below, slide to referral links—download link’s primed and waiting!
detailed.ms: Tak payah pening, boss! Ikon profil kat bawah, skrol ke pautan rujukan—pautan muat turun dah siap tunggu!
detailed.cn: 沒麻煩，老板！下方人頭圖標，滑到推薦鏈接，下載鏈接已備好等着您！

question.text: You bet, boss! You can use multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals—as long as they’re all under your name, you’ll have the freedom to manage your cash and enjoy the games to the fullest!
variations: Mesti boleh, boss! Boss boleh guna banyak akaun bank untuk deposit dan pengeluaran—selagi semua atas nama boss, boss bebas urus duit dan seronok main game sepenuhnya!
You bet, boss! You can use multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals—as long as they’re all under your name, you’ll have the freedom to manage your cash and enjoy the games to the fullest!
當然可以，老板！您可以使用多個銀行賬戶進行存款和提款，只要這些賬戶都是您本人名下的即可。這讓您在管理資金時更加靈活，盡情享受遊戲的樂趣！

languages.en: Can I use multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan beberapa akaun bank untuk deposit dan pengeluaran?
languages.cn: 我可以使用多個銀行賬戶進行存款和提款嗎？

detailed.en: Sure thing, boss! Multiple bank accounts work—just keep ‘em yours, and you’re golden for deposits and cash-outs!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Banyak akaun bank boleh—pastikan punya boss, dan boss selamat untuk deposit dan tarik keluar!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！多個銀行賬戶沒問題，只要是您的，存提款都隨心所欲！

question.text: Give it about 5-30 minutes before ringing support, boss—deposits usually wrap up in that time. If it’s still not there, hit me up—I’ll dig in and make sure you’re back gaming ASAP!
variations: Tunggu dalam 5-30 minit sebelum hubungi sokongan, boss—deposit biasanya selesai dalam masa tu. Kalau masih tak ada, bagitahu saya—saya selami pastikan boss boleh main balik cepat!
Give it about 5-30 minutes before ringing support, boss—deposits usually wrap up in that time. If it’s still not there, hit me up—I’ll dig in and make sure you’re back gaming ASAP!
在聯繫客服團隊之前，建議您等待大約5到30分鐘，老板。通常情況下，存款會在這個時間段內處理完畢。如果超過這個時間仍未到賬，隨時告訴我，我會幫您查明情況，確保您能順利繼續遊戲！

languages.en: How long should I wait for a deposit before contacting support?
languages.ms: Berapa lama saya harus menunggu untuk deposit sebelum menghubungi sokongan?
languages.cn: 在聯繫客服團隊之前，我應該等待存款多久？

detailed.en: Hang out 5-30 minutes, boss, before pinging support—deposits normally land then. Still nada? Holler, I’ll zap it through!
detailed.ms: Tahan 5-30 minit, boss, sebelum panggil sokongan—deposit biasanya masuk masa tu. Masih kosong? Jerit, saya hapuskan cepat!
detailed.cn: 等5-30分鐘，老板，再聯繫客服—存款通常那時到。還沒？喊我，我快幫您搞定！

question.text: No worries if you put the wrong reference on your deposit slip, boss! Next time, just make sure it’s spot on—it might slow down this one’s review, but your future moves are fine. Double-check everything next go-around!
variations: Tak risau kalau boss masukkan rujukan salah kat slip deposit! Lain kali, pastikan betul je—yang ni mungkin lambat sikit semak, tapi transaksi depan ok. Semak dua kali lepas ni!

No worries if you put the wrong reference on your deposit slip, boss! Next time, just make sure it’s spot on—it might slow down this one’s review, but your future moves are fine. Double-check everything next go-around!
若您在存款收據上輸入了錯誤的參考號，不用擔心，老板！下次存款時確保輸入正確的參考號即可。雖然這可能會影響當前存款的審核速度，但不影響您未來的交易。下次操作時請仔細檢查所有信息。

languages.en: I entered the wrong reference on my deposit receipt. How can I correct this?
languages.ms: Saya memasukkan rujukan yang salah pada resit deposit saya. Bagaimana saya boleh membetulkannya?
languages.cn: 我在存款收據上輸入了錯誤的參考號。我如何更正？

detailed.en: Chill, boss! Wrong reference? Nail it next time—this one might crawl, but you’re good later. Check twice next round!
detailed.ms: Tenang, boss! Rujukan salah? Betulkan lain kali—yang ni mungkin merangkak, tapi lepas ni ok. Semak dua kali nanti!
detailed.cn: 別急，老板！參考號錯了？下次弄對—this one可能慢點，但之後沒事。下一輪檢查仔細哦！

question.text: We can’t pin down if Maybank’s got maintenance issues, boss—if your transfer’s flopping, it’s usually maintenance or an update. Check Maybank’s official site for the latest scoop!
variations: Kami tak boleh pastikan kalau Maybank ada masalah penyelenggaraan, boss—kalau pindahan boss tak jadi, biasanya tengah selenggara atau update. Tengok laman rasmi Maybank untuk info terkini!
We can’t pin down if Maybank’s got maintenance issues, boss—if your transfer’s flopping, it’s usually maintenance or an update. Check Maybank’s official site for the latest scoop!
關於Maybank交易是否存在維護問題，我們無法確定具體情況，老板。若您發現Maybank轉賬不成功，通常是因為系統正在進行維護或更新。我建議您查看Maybank的官方網站，了解最新的維護信息。

languages.en: Is there a maintenance issue with Maybank transactions?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat masalah penyelenggaraan dengan transaksi Maybank?
languages.cn: Maybank交易是否存在維護問題？

detailed.en: Can’t tell, boss! Maybank transfers crashing? Likely maintenance or updates—hit their site for the dirt!
detailed.ms: Tak tahu, boss! Pindahan Maybank gagal? Mungkin tengah selenggara atau update—cek laman dia untuk scoop!
detailed.cn: 不清楚，老板！Maybank轉賬不順？多半在維護或更新，去官網挖最新消息吧！

question.text: You bet we’ve got some sweet promos and bonuses today, boss! Tap the megaphone icon up top in the app—latest deals are there so you don’t miss out on the good stuff!
variations: Mesti ada promosi dan bonus best hari ni, boss! Tekan ikon megafon kat atas app—tawaran terkini ada kat situ supaya boss tak terlepas benda baik!
You bet we’ve got some sweet promos and bonuses today, boss! Tap the megaphone icon up top in the app—latest deals are there so you don’t miss out on the good stuff!
今天我們確實有一些特別的促銷和獎勵活動，老板！您可以在應用程序上方的小喇叭圖標中查看最新的促銷信息，確保不錯過任何精彩的優惠。

languages.en: Are there any special promotions or bonuses available today?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat promosi atau bonus istimewa pada hari ini?
languages.cn: 今天有沒有特別的促銷或獎金活動？

detailed.en: Oh yeah, boss! Hot promos and bonuses today—hit the megaphone up top, snag all the juicy deals!
detailed.ms: Oh ya, boss! Promosi dan bonus panas hari ni—tekan megafon kat atas, tangkap semua tawaran sedap!
detailed.cn: 當然有，老板！今天促銷和獎金火熱，點上方小喇叭，搶所有好優惠哦！

question.text: If a game’s flashing ‘not available,’ boss, it’s likely under maintenance or getting a tweak—we’ll sort it quick. Hang tight and try again later to see if it’s back online!
variations: Kalau game tunjuk ‘tak tersedia,’ boss, mungkin tengah selenggara atau kena tweak—kami selesai cepat. Sabar jap dan cuba lagi nanti tengok dah ok ke belum!
If a game’s flashing ‘not available,’ boss, it’s likely under maintenance or getting a tweak—we’ll sort it quick. Hang tight and try again later to see if it’s back online!
如果遊戲顯示‘不可用’，老板，這可能是因為該遊戲正在進行維修或更新。我們會盡快處理這些維護工作。請您稍後再試，看看是否可以恢復訪問。

languages.en: What should I do if a game is showing as 'not available'?
languages.ms: Apa yang harus saya lakukan jika permainan menunjukkan "tidak tersedia"?
languages.cn: 如果遊戲顯示“不可用”，我應該怎麼做？

detailed.en: Yo, boss! Game says ‘not available’? Probably getting a fix—chill a bit, retry soon, should be live!
detailed.ms: Oi, boss! Game cakap ‘tak tersedia’? Mungkin tengah baiki—relax sikit, cuba balik nanti, patut hidup!
detailed.cn: 嘿，老板！遊戲顯示‘不可用’？可能在修，等一會兒再試，應該就好了！

question.text: You bet, boss! Swap your phone number anytime—tap the profile icon at the app’s bottom, pick the phone change option, and update it smooth!
variations: Mesti boleh, boss! Tukar nombor telefon bila-bila—tekan ikon profil kat bawah app, pilih pilihan tukar telefon, kemas kini dengan lancar!
You bet, boss! Swap your phone number anytime—tap the profile icon at the app’s bottom, pick the phone change option, and update it smooth!
當然可以，老板！您可以隨時更改與您賬戶相關的手機號碼。請點擊應用程序下方的人頭圖標，然後選擇更換手機號碼的選項進行更新。

languages.en: Is it possible to change the phone number associated with my account?
languages.ms: Adakah mungkin untuk menukar nombor telefon yang dikaitkan dengan akaun saya?
languages.cn: 我可以更改與我賬戶相關的手機號碼嗎？

detailed.en: Sure can, boss! New phone number? Hit profile at the bottom, change it up, slick and easy!
detailed.ms: Boleh lah, boss! Nombor telefon baru? Tekan profil kat bawah, tukar je, licin dan senang!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！新手機號？點下方人頭，換一換，順滑又簡單！

question.text: No canceling sports bets once they’re in, boss—odds shift live, so it’s locked to keep it fair for everyone. No take-backs here!
variations: Tak boleh batal pertaruhan sukan lepas dah masuk, boss—odds berubah secara langsung, jadi kunci untuk jaga adil semua orang. Tak ada tarik balik sini!
No canceling sports bets once they’re in, boss—odds shift live, so it’s locked to keep it fair for everyone. No take-backs here!
關於體育投注，一旦您下單後是無法取消的，老板，因為賽事的賠率是實時更新的。為了確保每位玩家都能享受公平的遊戲體驗，我們不支持取消已下的投注。

languages.en: Is there a way to cancel a sports bet I've placed?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat cara untuk membatalkan pertaruhan sukan yang telah saya buat?
languages.cn: 我可以取消已下的體育投注嗎？

detailed.en: No dice, boss! Sports bets stick once placed—live odds lock it, keeping it fair, no backsies!
detailed.ms: Tak boleh, boss! Pertaruhan sukan lekat lepas taruh—odds langsung kunci, jaga adil, tak ada undur!
detailed.cn: 不行，老板！體育投注下了就定了，實時賠率鎖住，公平起見，沒得退哦！

question.text: We can’t say for sure if Maybank’s got maintenance woes, boss—if your transfer’s tanking, it’s usually that or an update tweak. Scope out Maybank’s official site for the freshest intel!
variations: Kami tak pasti kalau Maybank ada masalah penyelenggaraan, boss—kalau pindahan boss tak jadi, biasanya tu atau ada tweak update. Cek laman rasmi Maybank untuk info paling baru!
We can’t say for sure if Maybank’s got maintenance woes, boss—if your transfer’s tanking, it’s usually that or an update tweak. Scope out Maybank’s official site for the freshest intel!
關於Maybank交易是否存在維護問題，我們無法確認具體情況，老板。若您在使用Maybank進行轉賬時遇到困難，通常是因為系統正在維護或更新。我建議您查看Maybank的官方網站，以獲取最新的維護信息。

languages.en: Is there a maintenance issue with Maybank transactions?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat masalah penyelenggaraan dengan transaksi Maybank?
languages.cn: Maybank交易是否存在維護問題？

detailed.en: No idea, boss! Maybank transfers bombing? Likely maintenance or an update—hit their site for the latest!
detailed.ms: Tak tahu lah, boss! Pindahan Maybank tak jadi? Mungkin selenggara atau update—tengok laman dia untuk terkini!
detailed.cn: 不清楚，老板！Maybank轉賬失敗？多半在維護或更新，去官網查最新吧！

question.text: No panic if you slipped up with the wrong ID on your deposit receipt, boss! It might slow this one’s review, but your next moves are safe—just triple-check everything next time to keep it smooth!
variations: Tak payah panik kalau boss tersilap masukkan nombor ID salah kat resit deposit! Mungkin lambat sikit semak yang ni, tapi transaksi depan selamat—cek tiga kali lepas ni supaya lancar!
No panic if you slipped up with the wrong ID on your deposit receipt, boss! It might slow this one’s review, but your next moves are safe—just triple-check everything next time to keep it smooth!
若您在存款收據上輸入了錯誤的ID號碼，首先不要擔心，老板！這可能會影響您當前存款的審核速度，但不會影響未來交易。請您下次存款時，仔細檢查所有信息，避免再次出錯。

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong ID number on my deposit receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan nombor ID yang salah pada resit deposit saya?
languages.cn: 如果我在存款收據上輸入了錯誤的ID號碼，我應該怎麼做？

detailed.en: No sweat, boss! Wrong ID on the receipt? Might drag this review, but you’re cool next time—check it thrice!
detailed.ms: Tak risau, boss! ID salah kat resit? Mungkin lambat semak kali ni, tapi ok lain kali—semak tiga kali!
detailed.cn: 別慌，老板！收據ID錯了？這次審核可能慢，但下次沒事—三檢查哦！

question.text: Account balances usually refresh right after a game wraps, boss! If it’s not updating, send me some screenshots—I’ll zip in and make sure it’s all squared up quick!
variations: Baki akaun biasanya segarkan sebaik game habis, boss! Kalau tak kemas kini, hantar screenshot—saya masuk cepat pastikan semua betul laju!
Account balances usually refresh right after a game wraps, boss! If it’s not updating, send me some screenshots—I’ll zip in and make sure it’s all squared up quick!
遊戲結束後，賬戶餘額通常會立即更新，老板！若您在遊戲結束後發現餘額未更新，請提供相關截圖信息，我會幫您查明情況。

languages.en: How often are account balances updated after a game session?
languages.ms: Berapa kerap baki akaun dikemas kini selepas sesi permainan?
languages.cn: 遊戲結束後，賬戶餘額多久更新一次？

detailed.en: Hey, boss! Balances pop fresh post-game—if it’s stuck, screenshots my way, I’ll blast it right!
detailed.ms: Hai, boss! Baki muncul baru lepas game—kalau tersangkut, hantar skrin, saya hapuskan betul cepat!
detailed.cn: 您好，老板！遊戲完餘額即刻刷，若卡住，截圖給我，我快幫您弄好！

question.text: We don’t usually dish out tax statements, boss—if the bank’s asking, just say it’s a loan, repayment, or item trade, keeps it simple!
variations: Kami biasanya tak bagi penyata cukai, boss—kalau bank tanya, cakap je pinjaman, bayar balik, atau urusan jual beli, senang je!
We don’t usually dish out tax statements, boss—if the bank’s asking, just say it’s a loan, repayment, or item trade, keeps it simple!
通常情況下，我們不會提供稅單，老板。若銀行問起，您可以說明這是借款、還款或買賣物品的相關交易。

languages.en: Can I request a tax statement for my winnings and losses?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya meminta penyata cukai untuk kemenangan dan kerugian saya?
languages.cn: 我可以要求提供我的獲利和損失的稅單嗎？

detailed.en: No tax sheets, boss! Bank curious? Call it a loan, payback, or trade—nice and easy!
detailed.ms: Tak ada penyata cukai, boss! Bank tanya? Cakap pinjaman, bayar balik, atau jual beli—mudah je!
detailed.cn: 沒稅單，老板！銀行問？說是借款、還款或交易，簡單又方便！

question.text: No can do, boss—one receipt, one top-up! If we catch it reused, the system’ll block it—keep it fresh with a new receipt each time for smooth moves!
variations: Tak boleh, boss—satu resit, satu tambah nilai je! Kalau kami nampak guna semula, sistem halang—pastikan baru setiap kali untuk lancar!
No can do, boss—one receipt, one top-up! If we catch it reused, the system’ll block it—keep it fresh with a new receipt each time for smooth moves!
不可以哦，老板！同一張收據只能用於一次充值。若我們發現該收據已被使用過，系統將不會通過該存款申請。在進行充值時，請確保使用新的收據，以確保交易順利進行。

languages.en: Can I use the same receipt for multiple top-ups?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan resit yang sama untuk beberapa tambah nilai?
languages.cn: 我可以使用同一張收據進行多次充值嗎？

detailed.en: No go, boss! One receipt per top-up—repeats get nixed. New one each time, smooth sailing!
detailed.ms: Tak jadi, boss! Satu resit satu tambah nilai—ulang kena buang. Baru setiap kali, lancar je!
detailed.cn: 不行，老板！一張收據一次充值，重複被拒。每次新收據，順利無阻！

question.text: Yep, boss—Mega888’s got an iOS version ready! Hit ‘More Games,’ pick slots, find the Mega888 icon—scroll down, tap the download option, and you’re set to install it easy!
variations: Ya, boss—Mega888 ada versi iOS siap! Tekan ‘Lebih Banyak Permainan,’ pilih slot, cari ikon Mega888—skrol bawah, tekan pilihan muat turun, senang je pasang!
Yep, boss—Mega888’s got an iOS version ready! Hit ‘More Games,’ pick slots, find the Mega888 icon—scroll down, tap the download option, and you’re set to install it easy!
是的，老板，Mega888確實有iOS版本的應用程序！您只需在‘更多遊戲’中選擇老虎機，然後找到Mega888的圖標。在頁面下方就能看到Mega888下載的選項，點擊即可輕鬆下載安裝。

languages.en: Is there an iOS version of the Mega888 app available?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat versi iOS untuk aplikasi Mega888?
languages.cn: Mega888有iOS版本的應用程序嗎？

detailed.en: You bet, boss! Mega888 iOS is live—‘More Games,’ slots, Mega888 icon, download tap, bam, installed!
detailed.ms: Mesti ada, boss! Mega888 iOS dah hidup—‘Lebih Banyak Permainan,’ slot, ikon Mega888, tekan muat turun, bam, pasang!
detailed.cn: 當然有，老板！Mega888 iOS版已備，‘更多遊戲’，選老虎機，Mega888圖標，點下載，砰，裝好！

question.text: Sure, boss—a small transfer’s a clever trick to check your account’s humming along fine! Pick a little cash, send it, and see it glide through safe and easy!
variations: Boleh, boss—pindahan kecil trik pandai nak semak akaun boss jalan elok! Pilih duit sikit, hantar, tengok masuk selamat dan senang!
Sure, boss—a small transfer’s a clever trick to check your account’s humming along fine! Pick a little cash, send it, and see it glide through safe and easy!
當然可以，老板！進行小額轉賬是一個非常聰明的方法來驗證您的賬戶是否正常運作。您可以選擇少量資金進行轉賬，既安全又方便。

languages.en: Can I make a small transfer to verify if my account is working correctly?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya membuat pemindahan kecil untuk mengesahkan jika akaun saya berfungsi dengan betul?
languages.cn: 我可以進行小額轉賬以驗證我的賬戶是否正常運作嗎？

detailed.en: You got it, boss! Small transfer’s a slick move—drop a bit, watch it flow, account’s golden!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Pindahan kecil gerakan licin—letak sikit, tengok mengalir, akaun boss mantap!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！小額轉賬聰明招，放點錢，看它流，賬戶穩穩當當！

question.text: I get why you’re sweating that approved withdrawal not hitting your bank yet, boss! It’s usually there in 5-30 minutes—might be a bank lag or system rush slowing it. Check your bank account—if it’s still missing past 30, send me screenshots—I’ll zip in and lock it down safe!
variations: Saya faham kenapa boss risau pengeluaran dah lulus tapi tak masuk bank lagi! Biasanya sampai dalam 5-30 minit—mungkin bank lambat atau sistem sibuk buat perlahan. Semak akaun bank boss—kalau masih hilang lepas 30, hantar screenshot—saya masuk kunci selamat cepat!

I get why you’re sweating that approved withdrawal not hitting your bank yet, boss! It’s usually there in 5-30 minutes—might be a bank lag or system rush slowing it. Check your bank account—if it’s still missing past 30, send me screenshots—I’ll zip in and lock it down safe!
我理解您對提款未入賬的擔憂，老板！通常情況下，一旦提款被批准，資金會在5到30分鐘內到賬。但有時可能因銀行處理延遲或系統繁忙而稍有延遲。請先檢查銀行賬戶，若超過30分鐘仍未收到，隨時提供截圖信息，我會幫您查明情況，確保資金安全！

languages.en: Why has my withdrawal been approved but not credited to my bank account?
languages.ms: Kenapa pengeluaran saya telah diluluskan tetapi belum dikreditkan ke akaun bank saya?
languages.cn: 為什麼我的提款已經被批准但沒有入賬到我的銀行賬戶？

detailed.en: Yo, boss! Approved withdrawal not in? Should hit 5-30—bank or system jam maybe. Check it, still gone? Screenshots, I’ll blitz it safe!
detailed.ms: Oi, boss! Pengeluaran lulus tak masuk? Patut 5-30—bank atau sistem sesak mungkin. Semak, masih tak ada? Hantar skrin, saya hapuskan selamat!
detailed.cn: 嘿，老板！提款批了沒到？該5-30分鐘，銀行或系統忙也許。查下，還沒？截圖給我，我快保您安全！

question.text: Updating your contact info’s a snap if it’s changed, boss! Tap the profile icon at the app’s bottom, head to profile settings—tweak your email and phone number there easy!
variations: Kemas kini maklumat hubungan senang je kalau dah berubah, boss! Tekan ikon profil kat bawah app, pergi tetapan profil—ubah emel dan nombor telefon boss kat situ mudah!
Updating your contact info’s a snap if it’s changed, boss! Tap the profile icon at the app’s bottom, head to profile settings—tweak your email and phone number there easy!
若您的聯繫信息發生更改，可以輕鬆更新，老板！請點擊應用程序下方的人頭圖標，然後找到個人資料設置，在這裡您可以更改您的郵箱和手機號碼。

languages.en: How do I update my contact information if it has changed?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mengemas kini maklumat hubungan saya jika ia telah berubah?
languages.cn: 如果我的聯繫信息發生更改，我如何更新？

detailed.en: No fuss, boss! Contact info shifted? Profile icon below, settings—swap email and phone, slick as that!
detailed.ms: Tak payah pening, boss! Maklumat hubungan berubah? Ikon profil kat bawah, tetapan—tukar emel dan telefon, licin macam tu!
detailed.cn: 沒麻煩，老板！聯繫信息變了？下方人頭，進設置—換郵箱和手機號，順滑得很！

question.text: I totally get why you’re scratching your head about that Fast Payment top-up not showing, boss! It usually pops up quick—if it’s not there yet, the system’s still chewing on it. Wait a bit, about 5-30 minutes—if it’s still missing, check your bank transfer log to make sure it went through. No dice? Send me screenshots, and I’ll sort it fast!
variations: Saya faham sangat kenapa boss garu kepala pasal tambah nilai Fast Payment tu tak keluar! Biasanya cepat muncul—kalau belum ada, sistem tengah proses. Tunggu sikit, dalam 5-30 minit—kalau masih tak nampak, semak log pindahan bank boss pastikan dah masuk. Tak ada? Hantar screenshot, saya selesai cepat!

I totally get why you’re scratching your head about that Fast Payment top-up not showing, boss! It usually pops up quick—if it’s not there yet, the system’s still chewing on it. Wait a bit, about 5-30 minutes—if it’s still missing, check your bank transfer log to make sure it went through. No dice? Send me screenshots, and I’ll sort it fast!
我理解您對快速支付充值未顯示在賬戶中的困惑，老板！通常情況下，充值會在短時間內自動更新。如果尚未顯示，可能是因為系統正在處理您的交易。請稍等片刻，通常需要5到30分鐘。如果超過這個時間仍未更新，請檢查銀行的轉賬記錄，確保一切順利。如問題依然存在，請提供截圖信息，我會幫您查明情況！

languages.en: Why isn't my Fast Payment top-up showing in my account?
languages.ms: Kenapa tambah nilai Fast Payment saya tidak dipaparkan dalam akaun saya?
languages.cn: 為什麼我的快速支付充值沒有顯示在賬戶中？

detailed.en: Hey, boss! Fast Payment top-up AWOL? Should zip in soon—system’s grinding, 5-30 minutes. Still nada? Bank log, then screenshots, I’ll blitz it!
detailed.ms: Hai, boss! Tambah nilai Fast Payment hilang? Patut masuk cepat—sistem tengah kerja, 5-30 minit. Masih kosong? Log bank, lepas tu screenshot, saya hapuskan laju!
detailed.cn: 您好，老板！快速充值不見？該快到，系統忙着，5-30分鐘。若還沒，查銀行記錄，然後截圖給我，我速解決！

question.text: I get why you’re antsy about those sports bet winnings not hitting yet, boss! They should drop in right after you exit the match—check your account balance first. If it’s still not there after 30 minutes, shoot me some screenshots—I’ll dig in and make sure your winnings land smooth!
variations: Saya faham kenapa boss tak sabar pasal kemenangan pertaruhan sukan tak masuk lagi! Patut masuk lepas boss keluar perlawanan—semak baki akaun boss dulu. Kalau masih tak ada lepas 30 minit, hantar screenshot—saya selami pastikan kemenangan boss sampai lancar!

I get why you’re antsy about those sports bet winnings not hitting yet, boss! They should drop in right after you exit the match—check your account balance first. If it’s still not there after 30 minutes, shoot me some screenshots—I’ll dig in and make sure your winnings land smooth!
我理解您對體育投注獎金未入賬的擔憂，老板！通常情況下，贏得的獎金會在您退出比賽後直接打入您的賬戶。如果您發現獎金沒有到賬，首先請檢查您的賬戶餘額。若30分鐘內仍未更新，請提供截圖信息，我會幫您查明情況，確保獎金順利到賬！

languages.en: My sports bet winnings haven't been credited. What should I do?
languages.ms: Kemenangan pertaruhan sukan saya belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
languages.cn: 我的體育投注獎金尚未入賬。我該怎麼辦？

detailed.en: Yo, boss! Sports winnings not in? Should hit post-match—peek at your balance. 30 minutes, still zip? Screenshots, I’ll zap it through!
detailed.ms: Oi, boss! Kemenangan sukan tak masuk? Patut masuk lepas game—tengok baki boss. 30 minit masih kosong? Hantar skrin, saya pacukan!
detailed.cn: 嘿，老板！體育獎金沒到？比賽後該進賬，查餘額。30分鐘還沒？截圖給我，我快幫您催！

question.text: Checking a pending withdrawal’s a breeze, boss! Just tap the wallet icon, pick ‘Transaction Records’—you’ll see all your withdrawal requests and their status, like ‘Pending’ or ‘Approved,’ right there!
variations: Semak status pengeluaran tertunda senang je, boss! Tekan ikon dompet, pilih ‘Rekod Transaksi’—boss akan tengok semua permintaan pengeluaran dan status dia, macam ‘Tertunda’ atau ‘Diluluskan,’ kat situ je!

Checking a pending withdrawal’s a breeze, boss! Just tap the wallet icon, pick ‘Transaction Records’—you’ll see all your withdrawal requests and their status, like ‘Pending’ or ‘Approved,’ right there!
要檢查待處理提款的狀態很簡單，老板！您只需點擊錢包圖標，然後選擇‘交易記錄’。在這裡，您可以查看所有的提款請求及其狀態，比如‘待處理’或‘已批准’。

languages.en: What's the process for checking the status of a pending withdrawal?
languages.ms: Apakah proses untuk memeriksa status pengeluaran yang tertunda?
languages.cn: 檢查待處理提款狀態的過程是什麼？

detailed.en: Easy, boss! Wallet icon, ‘Transaction Records’—pending or approved, it’s all laid out there!
detailed.ms: Senang je, boss! Ikon dompet, ‘Rekod Transaksi’—tertunda atau lulus, semua terbentang kat situ!
detailed.cn: 簡單，老板！錢包圖標，‘交易記錄’，待處理或已批，全在那兒一目了然！

question.text: Sure thing, boss! A small transfer’s a solid way to test if your account’s ticking along—pick any amount you want and send it to check everything’s running smooth!
variations: Boleh lah, boss! Pindahan kecil cara mantap nak test akaun boss jalan elok—pilih je jumlah yang boss nak dan hantar untuk semak semua lancar!
Sure thing, boss! A small transfer’s a solid way to test if your account’s ticking along—pick any amount you want and send it to check everything’s running smooth!
當然可以，老板！進行小額轉賬是一個很好的辦法來驗證您的賬戶是否正常運作。只需選擇您想要的金額進行轉賬，就能確保一切順利。

variations: Tarik dana balik ke akaun bank senang je, boss! Pastikan butiran bank boss dah masuk atas nama boss, lepas tu tekan ikon dompet, pilih ‘Pengeluaran,’ masukkan jumlah, tekan hantar—mudah macam tu je!
Getting funds back to your bank’s a snap, boss! Make sure your bank details are added under your name, then hit the wallet icon, pick ‘Withdraw,’ punch in your amount, and tap submit—easy as that!
提取資金回到您的銀行賬戶其實很簡單，老板！首先，請確保您已經添加了本人的銀行賬戶信息。然後，您只需點擊錢包圖標，選擇‘提款’，輸入您想要提取的金額，最後點擊提交即可。

languages.en: What's the process for withdrawing funds back to my bank account?
languages.ms: Apakah proses untuk mengeluarkan dana kembali ke akaun bank saya?
languages.cn: 將資金提取回我的銀行賬戶的流程是什麼？

detailed.en: Piece of cake, boss! Add your bank under your name, wallet icon, ‘Withdraw,’ set amount, submit—done!
detailed.ms: Senang je, boss! Masuk bank atas nama boss, ikon dompet, ‘Pengeluaran,’ set jumlah, hantar—siap!
detailed.cn: 簡單得很，老板！加您名下的銀行，錢包圖標，‘提款’，輸入金額，提交—搞定！

question.text: Good news, boss! No extra fees for deposits or withdrawals here—your money’s all yours to enjoy without sneaky costs piling up!
variations: Berita baik, boss! Tak ada yuran tambahan untuk deposit atau pengeluaran kat sini—duit boss semua untuk boss seronok tanpa kos sembunyi bertimbun!
Good news, boss! No extra fees for deposits or withdrawals here—your money’s all yours to enjoy without sneaky costs piling up!
好消息，老板！在我們這裡，存款和提款都沒有額外的相關費用。這意味著您可以盡情享受您的資金，無需擔心多餘的開銷。

languages.en: Are there any fees associated with deposits or withdrawals?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat yuran yang dikenakan untuk deposit atau pengeluaran?
languages.cn: 存款或提款是否有相關費用？

detailed.en: Sweet deal, boss! Deposits and withdrawals are fee-free—pure cash fun, no hidden bites!
detailed.ms: Deal manis, boss! Deposit dan pengeluaran bebas yuran—seronok duit tulen, tak ada gigit sembunyi!
detailed.cn: 好消息，老板！存提款零費用，純資金樂趣，沒隱藏扣款哦！

question.text: You bet, boss! On our platform, filtering games by provider or type is a breeze—just hit ‘More Games,’ and you’ll find a bunch of options to zero in on your faves quick!
variations: Mesti boleh, boss! Kat platform kami, tapis permainan ikut penyedia atau jenis senang je—tekan ‘Lebih Banyak Permainan,’ boss jumpa banyak pilihan untuk cari kegemaran cepat!
You bet, boss! On our platform, filtering games by provider or type is a breeze—just hit ‘More Games,’ and you’ll find a bunch of options to zero in on your faves quick!
當然可以，老板！在我們的平台上，您可以輕鬆按提供商或遊戲類型進行篩選。只需點擊‘更多遊戲’，然後您就能找到各種不同的篩選選項，讓您快速找到自己喜歡的遊戲。

languages.en: Is there a way to filter games by provider or type?
languages.ms: Adakah terdapat cara untuk menapis permainan mengikut penyedia atau jenis?
languages.cn: 是否可以按提供商或類型篩選遊戲？

detailed.en: Sure thing, boss! ‘More Games,’ filter by provider or type—snag your picks fast!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! ‘Lebih Banyak Permainan,’ tapis ikut penyedia atau jenis—tangkap pilihan boss laju!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！‘更多遊戲’，按提供商或類型篩，快找到您愛的遊戲！

question.text: If your Fast Payment top-up’s not popping up yet, boss, it’s likely the system’s still crunching it—usually takes a few minutes, up to 30 max. Peek at your bank transfer log to confirm it’s gone through—if it’s still a ghost after that, send me screenshots, I’ll zip it up safe!
variations: Kalau tambah nilai Fast Payment boss belum muncul, mungkin sistem tengah hancurkan—biasanya ambil beberapa minit, paling lama 30. Tengok log pindahan bank boss pastikan dah masuk—kalau masih tak ada lepas tu, hantar screenshot, saya selesai selamat cepat!

If your Fast Payment top-up’s not popping up yet, boss, it’s likely the system’s still crunching it—usually takes a few minutes, up to 30 max. Peek at your bank transfer log to confirm it’s gone through—if it’s still a ghost after that, send me screenshots, I’ll zip it up safe!
若您的快速支付充值尚未顯示在賬戶中，老板，可能是因為系統正在處理交易。這種情況一般會在幾分鐘內解決，但有時可能需要長達30分鐘。若超過這個時間仍未到賬，請查看您的銀行轉賬記錄，確認交易是否成功。如問題依舊，請提供截圖信息，我會幫您迅速查明情況，確保資金安全到位！

languages.en: Why isn't my Fast Payment top-up showing in my account?
languages.ms: Kenapa tambah nilai Fast Payment saya tidak dipaparkan dalam akaun saya?
languages.cn: 為什麼我的快速支付充值沒有顯示在賬戶中？

detailed.en: Hey, boss! Fast Payment top-up MIA? System’s chewing, few minutes to 30—check bank log. Still nada? Screenshots, I’ll lock it down quick!
detailed.ms: Hai, boss! Tambah nilai Fast Payment tak ada? Sistem tengah kunyah, beberapa minit sampai 30—semak log bank. Masih kosong? Hantar skrin, saya kunci laju!
detailed.cn: 您好，老板！快速充值不見？系統在消化，幾分鐘到30—查銀行記錄。還沒？截圖給我，我快保安全！

question.text: If the system’s asking you to wait 5 minutes for a transaction, boss, it’s usually ‘cause you’ve been firing off a bunch of the same moves fast—safety kick to keep all players secure. Chill for a bit, then try again after the timeout!
variations: Kalau sistem suruh boss tunggu 5 minit untuk transaksi, biasanya sebab boss dah buat banyak gerakan sama cepat—tendang keselamatan untuk jaga semua pemain selamat. Relax sikit, cuba lagi lepas masa tamat!

If the system’s asking you to wait 5 minutes for a transaction, boss, it’s usually ‘cause you’ve been firing off a bunch of the same moves fast—safety kick to keep all players secure. Chill for a bit, then try again after the timeout!
若系統要求您等待5分鐘進行交易，老板，通常是因為您進行了高頻率的相同交易。為了保障所有玩家的交易安全，我們會在這種情況下設置短暫的延遲。請您耐心等候，過了這段時間再嘗試進行交易。

languages.en: Why did the system ask me to wait 5 minutes for a transaction?
languages.ms: Kenapa sistem meminta saya menunggu 5 minit untuk transaksi?
languages.cn: 為什麼系統要求我等待5分鐘進行交易？

detailed.en: Yo, boss! 5-minute wait? You’ve been blazing same moves—safety brake’s on. Cool off, retry post-pause!
detailed.ms: Oi, boss! Tunggu 5 minit? Boss dah laju buat benda sama—brek keselamatan masuk. Sejuk jap, cuba balik lepas berhenti!
detailed.cn: 嘿，老板！等5分鐘？您頻頻同樣操作，安全剎車啟動。冷靜下，停後再試哦！

question.text: Hang on about 5-30 minutes before buzzing support, boss—that’s usually enough for the system to process your deposit. If it’s still not there, don’t hold back—hit me up, and I’ll dive in full force to track it down!
variations: Tahan dalam 5-30 minit sebelum hubungi sokongan, boss—biasanya cukup untuk sistem proses deposit boss. Kalau masih tak ada, jangan tahan—hubungi saya, saya masuk sepenuh tenaga cari!

Hang on about 5-30 minutes before buzzing support, boss—that’s usually enough for the system to process your deposit. If it’s still not there, don’t hold back—hit me up, and I’ll dive in full force to track it down!
在聯繫客服團隊之前，建議您等待大約5到30分鐘，老板。這段時間通常足夠系統處理您的存款。如果超過這個時間仍未到賬，別猶豫，直接告訴我，我會全力協助您查找原因。

languages.en: How long should I wait for a deposit before contacting support?
languages.ms: Berapa lama saya harus menunggu untuk deposit sebelum menghubungi sokongan?
languages.cn: 在聯繫客服團隊之前，我應該等待存款多久？

detailed.en: Chill 5-30 minutes, boss, before pinging support—deposit’s usually in by then. Still zip? Holler, I’ll hunt it down hard!
detailed.ms: Relax 5-30 minit, boss, sebelum panggil sokongan—deposit biasanya masuk masa tu. Masih kosong? Jerit, saya cari kuat!
detailed.cn: 等5-30分鐘，老板，再聯繫客服—存款通常那時到。還沒？喊我，我全力追查！

question.text: Checking your last week’s betting history is a piece of cake, boss! Open the app, tap the wallet icon, go to ‘Transaction Records’—filter it there, and all your betting details from the past week pop right up!
variations: Semak sejarah pertaruhan minggu lepas senang je, boss! Buka app, tekan ikon dompet, pergi ‘Rekod Transaksi’—tapis kat situ, semua butiran pertaruhan minggu lepas muncul terus!

Checking your last week’s betting history is a piece of cake, boss! Open the app, tap the wallet icon, go to ‘Transaction Records’—filter it there, and all your betting details from the past week pop right up!
查看您過去一周的投注記錄其實很簡單，老板！您只需打開應用程序，點擊錢包圖標，然後找到‘交易記錄’，在這裡您可以輕鬆篩選出過去一周的所有投注詳情。

languages.en: How can I check my betting history for the past week?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh memeriksa sejarah pertaruhan saya untuk minggu lepas?
languages.cn: 如何查看我過去一周的投注記錄？

detailed.en: No sweat, boss! App, wallet icon, ‘Transaction Records’—filter last week, bets all there easy!
detailed.ms: Tak susah, boss! App, ikon dompet, ‘Rekod Transaksi’—tapis minggu lepas, pertaruhan semua ada senang!
detailed.cn: 輕鬆，老板！應用，錢包圖標，‘交易記錄’，篩上周，投注全顯簡單得很！

question.text: If you drop out during a live game, boss, don’t sweat it! Reconnect your network and log back in—you’ll usually land right where you left off, bets still good to go!
variations: Kalau terputus tengah main game langsung, boss, tak payah risau! Sambung balik rangkaian dan log masuk semula—biasanya boss balik kat tempat tinggal tadi, pertaruhan masih ok!
If you drop out during a live game, boss, don’t sweat it! Reconnect your network and log back in—you’ll usually land right where you left off, bets still good to go!
若您在遊戲過程中斷線，老板，不用擔心！請嘗試重新連接網絡並重新登錄遊戲。大部分情況下，您會恢復到您離開的地方，您的投注應該會保持有效。

languages.en: What should I do if I experience a disconnection during a live game?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mengalami terputus sambungan semasa permainan langsung?
languages.cn: 如果我在遊戲過程中斷線，應該怎麼做？

detailed.en: Hey, boss! Disconnect mid-live game? Plug back in, relog—usually zaps you back, bets intact!
detailed.ms: Hai, boss! Putus tengah game langsung? Sambung balik, log masuk semula—biasanya bawa boss balik, taruhan selamat!
detailed.cn: 您好，老板！遊戲中斷線？重連，重登—多半帶您回原地，投注無損！

question.text: You bet, boss! ATM deposit receipts work just fine for top-ups—make sure you’re sending it to our bank account, and your top-up’s good to roll!
variations: Mesti boleh, boss! Resit deposit ATM ok je untuk tambah nilai—pastikan hantar ke akaun bank kami, tambah nilai boss siap untuk jalan!
You bet, boss! ATM deposit receipts work just fine for top-ups—make sure you’re sending it to our bank account, and your top-up’s good to roll!
是的，老板，ATM存款收據是可以作為充值的有效憑證！只需確保您是按照我們提供的銀行賬戶進行匯款，這樣您的充值請求就能順利處理。

languages.en: Are ATM deposit receipts accepted for top-ups?
languages.ms: Adakah resit deposit ATM diterima untuk tambah nilai?
languages.cn: ATM存款收據是否被接受作為充值？

detailed.en: Sure thing, boss! ATM receipts are gold for top-ups—just aim it at our bank, and you’re set!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Resit ATM mantap untuk tambah nilai—hantar je ke bank kami, boss dah siap!
detailed.cn: 當然可以，老板！ATM收據充值沒問題，照我們銀行賬戶匯，搞定！

question.text: Account balances usually update instantly after a game session ends, boss! If yours isn’t ticking over, send me some screenshots—I’ll zoom in and straighten it out fast!
variations: Baki akaun biasanya kemas kini sekejap lepas sesi game habis, boss! Kalau baki boss tak bergerak, hantar screenshot—saya zoom masuk betulkan cepat!
Account balances usually update instantly after a game session ends, boss! If yours isn’t ticking over, send me some screenshots—I’ll zoom in and straighten it out fast!
遊戲結束後，賬戶餘額通常會立即更新，老板！若您發現餘額未及時更新，請提供相關截圖信息，我會幫您核實情況。

languages.en: How often are account balances updated after a game session?
languages.ms: Berapa kerap baki akaun dikemas kini selepas sesi permainan?
languages.cn: 遊戲結束後，賬戶餘額多久更新一次？

detailed.en: Hey, boss! Balances flip fresh post-game—if it’s stuck, screenshots my way, I’ll blast it right!
detailed.ms: Hai, boss! Baki tukar baru lepas game—kalau tersangkut, hantar skrin, saya hapuskan betul!
detailed.cn: 您好，老板！遊戲完餘額即刻刷，若卡住，截圖給我，我快弄好！

question.text: No go, boss—using an old receipt for a new transaction’s off-limits! Each one’s a one-shot deal—system won’t let repeats fly. Grab a fresh receipt for each move to keep it legit!
variations: Tak boleh, boss—guna resit lama untuk transaksi baru tak dibenarkan! Satu resit satu kali je—sistem tak bagi ulang. Ambil resit baru setiap kali untuk kekal sah!
No go, boss—using an old receipt for a new transaction’s off-limits! Each one’s a one-shot deal—system won’t let repeats fly. Grab a fresh receipt for each move to keep it legit!
不行哦，老板，使用舊的收據進行新的交易是不被允許的！每張收據只能使用一次，若我們發現舊的收據已被使用過，系統將不會通過該存款請求。

languages.en: Can I use an older receipt for a new transaction?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan resit lama untuk transaksi baru?
languages.cn: 我可以用舊的收據進行新的交易嗎？

detailed.en: No dice, boss! Old receipts can’t roll new—one-time shot, system blocks repeats. Fresh one each time!
detailed.ms: Tak jadi, boss! Resit lama tak boleh main baru—sekali je, sistem halang ulang. Baru setiap kali!
detailed.cn: 不行，老板！舊收據不能新用，一次搞定，系統攔重複。每次新收據哦！

question.text: You won’t get a confirmation receipt right after uploading your deposit slip, boss—but you can check the status in your wallet’s ‘Transaction Records.’ That’s the best spot to confirm it’s all good!
variations: Boss tak akan dapat resit pengesahan terus lepas muat naik slip deposit—tapi boss boleh semak status kat ‘Rekod Transaksi’ dalam dompet. Tu tempat terbaik nak pastikan semua ok!
You won’t get a confirmation receipt right after uploading your deposit slip, boss—but you can check the status in your wallet’s ‘Transaction Records.’ That’s the best spot to confirm it’s all good!
上傳您的存款單後，您不會直接收到確認收據，老板，但您可以在錢包的‘交易記錄’中查看存款狀態。這是確認您交易是否成功的最佳方式。

languages.en: Will I receive a confirmation receipt after uploading my deposit slip?
languages.ms: Adakah saya akan menerima resit pengesahan selepas memuat naik slip deposit saya?
languages.cn: 上傳我的存款單後，我會收到確認收據嗎？

detailed.en: No receipt off the bat, boss! Post-upload, wallet’s ‘Transaction Records’—your go-to for the green light!
detailed.ms: Tak ada resit sekejap, boss! Lepas muat naik, ‘Rekod Transaksi’ kat dompet—tempat boss cek lampu hijau!
detailed.cn: 沒即時收據，老板！上傳後，錢包‘交易記錄’—您確認順利的首選！

question.text: Sure can, boss! You’re free to use multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals—as long as they’re all in your name, you’ve got the wiggle room to manage your funds slick and easy!
variations: Boleh je, boss! Boss bebas guna banyak akaun bank untuk deposit dan pengeluaran—selagi semua atas nama boss, boss ada ruang untuk urus duit licin dan senang!
Sure can, boss! You’re free to use multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals—as long as they’re all in your name, you’ve got the wiggle room to manage your funds slick and easy!
當然可以，老板！您可以使用多個銀行賬戶進行存款和提款，只要這些賬戶都是您本人名下的就可以。這為您提供了更多的靈活性，方便您管理資金。

languages.en: Can I use multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan beberapa akaun bank untuk deposit dan pengeluaran?
languages.cn: 我可以使用多個銀行賬戶進行存款和提款嗎？

detailed.en: You got it, boss! Multiple bank accounts for deposits and withdrawals—keep ‘em yours, flex your cash smooth!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Banyak akaun bank untuk deposit dan pengeluaran—pastikan punya boss, urus duit lancar!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！多個銀行賬戶存提款，只要您的，資金管理順溜得很！

question.text: No demo mode on deck right now, boss—but no sweat! You can dive in with a small real-money bet instead, keeping the fun flowing and the risk low, super flexible!
variations: Tak ada mod demo buat masa ni, boss—tapi tak apa! Boss boleh masuk dengan pertaruhan kecil duit betul je, kekal seronok dan risiko rendah, fleksibel gila!
No demo mode on deck right now, boss—but no sweat! You can dive in with a small real-money bet instead, keeping the fun flowing and the risk low, super flexible!
目前我們並沒有提供演示模式供您試玩，但沒關係，老板！您可以選擇少量資金進行真錢投注，這樣既能體驗遊戲的樂趣，又能控制風險，非常靈活。

languages.en: Can I play games in demo mode before betting real money?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya bermain permainan dalam mod demo sebelum bertaruh dengan wang sebenar?
languages.cn: 在使用真錢投注之前，我可以先在演示模式中玩遊戲嗎？

detailed.en: No demo yet, boss! Jump in with a tiny real bet—fun’s on, risk’s low, flex it your way!
detailed.ms: Belum ada demo, boss! Masuk je dengan taruhan kecil duit betul—seronok hidup, risiko rendah, ikut cara boss!
detailed.cn: 還沒演示模式，老板！用小額真錢玩—樂趣開啟，風險小，隨您怎麼靈活！

question.text: Sorry, boss—old receipts won’t fly for new transactions! Each one’s a one-time ticket—if we spot a repeat, the system shuts it down. Fresh receipt every go!
variations: Maaf, boss—resit lama tak boleh guna untuk transaksi baru! Satu resit satu tiket je—kalau kami nampak ulang, sistem tutup. Resit baru setiap kali!
Sorry, boss—old receipts won’t fly for new transactions! Each one’s a one-time ticket—if we spot a repeat, the system shuts it down. Fresh receipt every go!
抱歉，老板，使用舊的收據進行新的交易是不允許的哦！若我們發現舊的收據已被使用過，系統將不會通過該存款請求。

languages.en: Can I use an older receipt for a new transaction?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan resit lama untuk transaksi baru?
languages.cn: 我可以用舊的收據進行新的交易嗎？

detailed.en: No can do, boss! Old receipts are dead for new moves—one-shot only, repeats get zapped!
detailed.ms: Tak boleh lah, boss! Resit lama mati untuk gerakan baru—sekali je, ulang kena zap!
detailed.cn: 不行，老板！舊收據新交易用不了，一次而已，重複就被拒哦！

question.text: No biggie if you keyed in the wrong password, boss—it happens! Tap ‘Forgot Password’ on the login page, follow the steps to reset, and you’ll be back in the game quick!
variations: Tak ada hal kalau boss masukkan kata laluan salah—biasa je! Tekan ‘Lupa Kata Laluan’ kat laman log masuk, ikut langkah untuk reset, boss balik main cepat!
No biggie if you keyed in the wrong password, boss—it happens! Tap ‘Forgot Password’ on the login page, follow the steps to reset, and you’ll be back in the game quick!
若您輸入了錯誤的密碼，不用擔心，老板，這種情況很常見！您可以點擊登錄頁面的‘忘記密碼’選項，按照提示重置密碼，就能迅速恢復您的賬戶訪問。

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong password?
languages.ms: Apa yang harus saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan kata laluan yang salah?
languages.cn: 如果輸入了錯誤的密碼，我應該怎麼做？

detailed.en: No stress, boss! Wrong password’s common—hit ‘Forgot Password’ on login, reset, back gaming fast!
detailed.ms: Tak tension, boss! Kata laluan salah biasa—tekan ‘Lupa Kata Laluan’ kat log masuk, reset, balik main laju!
detailed.cn: 別慌，老板！錯密碼常有，登錄頁點‘忘記密碼’，重設，速回遊戲哦！

question.text: Checking odds for upcoming sports events is a snap, boss! Open the app, hit ‘More Games,’ tap the football icon—all the upcoming football events and their odds are right there for you!

detailed.en: All set, boss! Two-factor’s on—password plus code, your account’s Fort Knox!
detailed.ms: Dah siap, boss! Dua faktor hidup—kata laluan tambah kod, akaun boss macam Fort Knox!
detailed.cn: 搞定了，老板！雙重驗證開啟—密碼加碼，您的賬戶固若金湯！

question.text: To chase an unapproved withdrawal request, boss, fire up the app, hit the wallet icon, check ‘Transaction Records’—you’ll see the status of all your withdrawal moves right there!
variations: Nak ikut permintaan pengeluaran belum lulus, boss, buka app, tekan ikon dompet, semak ‘Rekod Transaksi’—boss akan tengok status semua gerakan pengeluaran kat situ je!
To chase an unapproved withdrawal request, boss, fire up the app, hit the wallet icon, check ‘Transaction Records’—you’ll see the status of all your withdrawal moves right there!
要跟進尚未批准的提款請求，老板，您可以打開應用程序，點擊錢包圖標，然後查看您的‘交易記錄’。在那裡，您可以找到提款請求的狀態。

languages.en: How can I follow up on a withdrawal request that hasn't been approved?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh membuat susulan pada permintaan pengeluaran yang belum diluluskan?
languages.cn: 如何跟進尚未批准的提款請求？

detailed.en: Easy, boss! App, wallet, ‘Transaction Records’—track unapproved withdrawals right there!
detailed.ms: Senang je, boss! App, dompet, ‘Rekod Transaksi’—jejaki pengeluaran tak lulus kat situ je!
detailed.cn: 簡單，老板！應用，錢包，‘交易記錄’—未批提款狀態全在那！

question.text: Sorry, boss—old receipts don’t cut it for new transactions! Each one’s a one-time deal—if we spot it’s been used, no dice. Grab a fresh receipt next time to keep things smooth!
variations: Maaf, boss—resit lama tak boleh guna untuk transaksi baru! Satu resit satu kali je—kalau kami nampak dah guna, tak jadi. Ambil resit baru lain kali untuk jaga lancar!
Sorry, boss—old receipts don’t cut it for new transactions! Each one’s a one-time deal—if we spot it’s been used, no dice. Grab a fresh receipt next time to keep things smooth!
很抱歉，老板，舊的收據是不能用於新的交易的哦！每張收據只能使用一次，若我們發現該收據已被使用過，就無法再次進行交易。建議您下次存款時確保使用新收據，以確保交易順利。

languages.en: Can I use an older receipt for a new transaction?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan resit lama untuk transaksi baru?
languages.cn: 我可以用舊的收據進行新的交易嗎？

detailed.en: No go, boss! Old receipts won’t fly—one-shot only, repeats get zapped. Fresh one next time!
detailed.ms: Tak boleh, boss! Resit lama tak laku—sekali je, ulang kena zap. Baru lain kali!
detailed.cn: 不行，老板！舊收據用不了，一次而已，重複被拒。下次拿新的順利哦！

question.text: You bet, boss! Your e-wallet account number works fine for transactions—just tap the wallet icon, pick ‘Top Up,’ and you’ll see e-wallet under quick pay options. Smooth and simple!
variations: Boleh je, boss! Nombor akaun e-dompet boss ok untuk transaksi—tekan ikon dompet, pilih ‘Tambah Nilai,’ boss akan tengok e-dompet kat pilihan bayar cepat. Licin dan senang!
You bet, boss! Your e-wallet account number works fine for transactions—just tap the wallet icon, pick ‘Top Up,’ and you’ll see e-wallet under quick pay options. Smooth and simple!
當然可以，老板！您可以使用您的電子錢包賬號進行交易。只需點擊錢包圖標，然後選擇‘充值’，在這裡您會看到快速支付選項，其中包括電子錢包的支付方式。

languages.en: Can I use my e-wallet account number for transactions?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya menggunakan nombor akaun e-dompet saya untuk transaksi?
languages.cn: 我可以使用我的電子錢包賬號進行交易嗎？

detailed.en: Sure thing, boss! E-wallet number’s good—wallet, ‘Top Up,’ quick pay, e-wallet’s there, easy!
detailed.ms: Ok lah, boss! Nombor e-dompet boleh—dompet, ‘Tambah Nilai,’ bayar cepat, e-dompet ada, senang!
detailed.cn: 當然行，老板！電子錢包賬號可用—錢包，‘充值’，快付選項，電子錢包在，簡單！

question.text: No minimum age limit for signing up, boss! Got a smartphone and a connection? You’re good to roll and kick off your gaming adventure!
variations: Tak ada had umur minimum untuk daftar, boss! Ada telefon pintar dan sambungan? Boss dah boleh mula dan masuk adventure game!
No minimum age limit for signing up, boss! Got a smartphone and a connection? You’re good to roll and kick off your gaming adventure!
關於創建賬戶的最低年齡要求，老板，其實我們並沒有具體的限制！只要您擁有智能手機和網絡，就可以輕鬆註冊賬戶，開始您的遊戲之旅。

languages.en: What's the minimum age requirement for creating an account?
languages.ms: Berapakah umur minimum yang diperlukan untuk membuat akaun?
languages.cn: 創建賬戶的最低年齡要求是什麼？

detailed.en: No age bar, boss! Smartphone and net, you’re set—jump into gaming anytime!
detailed.ms: Tak ada batas umur, boss! Telefon pintar dan net, boss dah siap—lompat masuk game bila-bila!
detailed.cn: 無年齡限制，老板！智能手機和網絡，您就行—隨時開啟遊戲之旅！

question.text: For urgent stuff, boss, hit the online support icon at the bottom of the app—live help’s right there to tackle your issues on the spot!
variations: Kalau ada benda urgent, boss, tekan ikon sokongan online kat bawah app—bantuan langsung ada kat situ untuk selesai isu boss masa tu jugak!
For urgent stuff, boss, hit the online support icon at the bottom of the app—live help’s right there to tackle your issues on the spot!
若您遇到緊急問題，老板，可以通過應用程序底部的在線客服圖標直接聯繫實時支持。我們會在第一時間為您解答疑問，確保問題得到及時處理。

languages.en: How can I contact live support if I have urgent issues?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menghubungi sokongan langsung jika saya mempunyai isu yang mendesak?
languages.cn: 如果我有緊急問題，我如何聯繫實時支持？

detailed.en: Rush job, boss? App bottom, online support icon—live crew hits your issues fast!
detailed.ms: Tergesa, boss? Bawah app, ikon sokongan online—pasukan langsung selesai isu boss cepat!
detailed.cn: 急事，老板？應用底部，在線客服圖標—實時團隊速解您的問題！

question.text: Snagging the gaming app download link’s a cinch, boss! Tap the profile icon at the bottom of the app, slide to the bottom—bam, referral links section has the download link ready for you!
variations: Cari pautan muat turun app permainan senang je, boss! Tekan ikon profil kat bawah app, luncur ke bawah—bam, bahagian pautan rujukan ada link muat turun sedia untuk boss!
Snagging the gaming app download link’s a cinch, boss! Tap the profile icon at the bottom of the app, slide to the bottom—bam, referral links section has the download link ready for you!
找到遊戲應用程序的下載鏈接其實很簡單，老板！您只需點擊應用程序下方的人頭圖標，然後滑動到頁面底部，就能看到推薦鏈接，其中就有下載鏈接供您使用。

languages.en: Where can I find the download link for the gaming app?
languages.ms: Di manakah saya boleh mencari pautan muat turun untuk aplikasi permainan?
languages.cn: 我可以在哪裡找到遊戲應用程序的下載鏈接？

detailed.en: Dead easy, boss! Profile icon below, slide down—referral links, download’s waiting!
detailed.ms: Mudah gila, boss! Ikon profil kat bawah, luncur bawah—pautan rujukan, muat turun tunggu boss!
detailed.cn: 超簡單，老板！下方人頭圖標，滑到底，推薦鏈接裡的下載等着您！

question.text: No stress if you punched in the wrong password, boss! Hit ‘Forgot Password’ on the login page, follow the prompts to reset, and you’ll be back in action lickety-split!
variations: Tak tension kalau boss masukkan kata laluan salah! Tekan ‘Lupa Kata Laluan’ kat laman log masuk, ikut arahan untuk reset, boss balik beraksi cepat je!
No stress if you punched in the wrong password, boss! Hit ‘Forgot Password’ on the login page, follow the prompts to reset, and you’ll be back in action lickety-split!
若您輸入了錯誤的密碼，不用擔心，老板！您可以在登錄頁面點擊‘忘記密碼’選項，按照提示重置密碼，就能輕鬆恢復對賬戶的訪問。

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong password?
languages.ms: Apa yang harus saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan kata laluan yang salah?
languages.cn: 如果輸入了錯誤的密碼，我應該怎麼做？

detailed.en: No sweat, boss! Wrong password? ‘Forgot Password’ on login, reset steps, back in fast!
detailed.ms: Tak risau, boss! Kata laluan salah? ‘Lupa Kata Laluan’ kat log masuk, langkah reset, balik cepat!
detailed.cn: 別急，老板！密碼錯了？登錄頁‘忘記密碼’，按步驟重設，速回來！
